obligation to consult with property owners by holding a public meeting and consulting with
the persons who appear at that meeting, as long as notice has been sent to each property
owner as required in section 901.
Sec. 3. 38 MRSA §902, sub-§1-A, as corrected by RR 2013, c. 2, §48, is amended
to read:
1-A. Extension of consultation period. The consultation period under subsection 1
must be extended for an additional 180 210 days if:
